{"type": "article", "id": 19151, "title": "黑武士和帝国突击兵的咖啡杯盖", "description": "", "date": "2015-12-16T07:32:54Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 48, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702134740CW3B8i9pbGa0xU4L.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t<a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/14027.html\" target=\"_blank\">我们曾经报道过有亲吻感觉的咖啡杯盖，</a>这里是类似的概念。来自美国设计师 Spencer Davis 和 Scott Schenone，他们用了黑武士和帝国突击兵的元素，一黑一白，都在嘴巴的位置空出了一个散热和喝水的小口，让你在喝的时候有了亲吻的感觉，也是一种特别的互动。产品目前只是概念，却是一个不错的广告营销。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726145759WDHaMrfovSiI1QGw.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"1481\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"2.3140625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261458007LavZU3oG6yXfgSz.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"2519\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"3.9359375\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726145801KNIEG8gYpzq7Qncj.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"1641\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"2.5640625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}